^5Help - Set TalkMode
~5USAGE: .set talkmode [^5on~5/^5off~5]

~5Use this command when you wish to toggle between being in talk mode (that
~5is, you must put a ^.^ before a command), and in command mode (that is,
~5you don't put a ^.^ before the command--just type it in).

~5SEE ALSO
  ^5.help set

